{"tid":2129931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「塔羅」NobleMan Tarot 任追唔嬲 78張完整Arcana","createTime":"2020-07-29T02:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T17:44:46.000Z","uid":335921,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ad41140da2b8cd1feb50cbc22d80be80bc5af77b","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"塔羅牌自15世紀於歐洲各國流傳，較常見嘅塔羅牌係由22張被稱為大阿爾克那 (Major Arcana) 嘅牌組成，而較完整嘅塔羅就會包含埋共56張嘅小阿爾克那 (Minor Arcana)<br />\n<br />\nMajor Arcana 每張牌嘅象徵意義較強，例如死神、命運之輪、戀人之類，但同時亦比較闊，而Minor Arcana就大大咁增加左塔羅占卜嘅深度同用途。<br />\n<br />\nMinor Arcana由 權杖、寶劍、聖杯 同 金幣組成，各對應住 火、風、水、地 四個煉金術元素，更加有元素牌，宮廷牌之分。為左更加具體同詳細嘅占卜，本人所有占卜都會用曬78張塔羅進行。<br />\n<br />\n過去依三四年幫過自己，同埋唔少嘅朋友，新相識嘅人占卜過，得到嘅反應都唔錯，所以決定係連登依到同大家分享下塔羅牌依樣野。<br />\n<br />\n到底塔羅牌有冇用？係咪真係可以預知未來？就本人而言，見仁見智，讀科學出身嘅我唔會話一張牌可以改寫到人嘅命運，從來書寫命運嘅只有自己。<br />\n<br />\n但相對地，塔羅於我更加似係一種心靈治療，心理鼓勵嘅媒介，往往當你問一個問題，其實心中早已有一個答案，或者你冇意識到，或者你只係需要一個鼓勵去相信自己，而我希望通過塔羅牌，令你可以搵到你嘅答案。<br />\n<br />\n每日我都會處理大約十至十五個新嘅問題，亦唔介意大家無限追問牌陣嘅解答，盡可能地我會先答新嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n占卜主要用「聖三角牌陣」 去做，三張牌分別代表事情嘅「過去&amp;起因」，「現在&amp;可能行動」，「預想&amp;建議」<br />\n<br />\n問題請以以下嘅格式提出：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>稱呼 <br />\n1)姓別<br />\n2)年齡層 <br />\n3)問題<br />\n4)其他你覺得會有用嘅資料<br />\n如果牽涉到其他人的話，最好有一樣嘅基礎資訊。<br />\n5)然後係 1-78 選 3 個數字 （唔一定順大小，我會跟你數字嘅牌序抽牌）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n基本上任何問題都可以試下問，如果占唔到的話，我都會解釋返比你聽。<br />\n但有啲問題就真係幾難搞，例如生死，N年後嘅事，對象姓咩幾歲，黎緊幾時有拖拍。<br />\n生死 - 自問無力參透生死。<br />\nN年後嘅事 - 正如我一開始，書寫命運係人嘅事，未來太多變數<br />\n對象姓咩幾歲 - 塔羅好少會有象徵數字/文字嘅牌<br />\n幾時有拖拍 - 同上，但可以睇下有冇姻緣出現<br />\n所以各位諗諗先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，為左改善我嘅占卜水平，希望各位係收到結果後，簡單講返準唔準，最重要係你覺得有冇用。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎參與Nobleman Tarot Beta<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408f0304a58c1e2bc2bd889724666ab923c9d289","tid":2129931,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f7f37e5c9a79db35cf1a5a42beb0b6c3117d6e","tid":2129931,"uid":246817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96926385063b70910e52bc803c50b20ef6c82400","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764baa10f30f4026da7281a03dfe24792440b115","tid":2129931,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3d81a07c68638a711fb11eedeceb512752d888","tid":2129931,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764baa10f30f4026da7281a03dfe24792440b115","tid":2129931,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2262fa0287f667414345da6736e958efe5fe14d8","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04f7f37e5c9a79db35cf1a5a42beb0b6c3117d6e","tid":2129931,"uid":246817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"三張牌分別係 金幣五正 權杖騎士逆 權杖四正<br />\n<br />\n金幣五出現象徵貧窮，相信兩位並唔係啲咩大富大貴嘅人，都只係學生/手停口停嘅打工仔，過去一直有關於現實生活，前境之類嘅問題困擾住大家嘅關係，但同時地大家都係能夠互相扶持走過咗一段日子。<br />\n<br />\n但象徵熱情/憤怒嘅權杖騎士反映咗你地係一次爭執中分開咗，二人當中有一方往往比較耐不住氣，係困難前比較情緒化，缺乏耐性去共渡難關，積累落黎嘅矛盾爆發開黎導致分手。<br />\n<br />\n權杖四正象徵分享同享受，但前提係要先排除到現實手活上嘅問題，大家更多地分享彼此想法，係努力下其實係會有復合嘅可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69a4efcf3ea3dad0144a3f2585190a531dd2233","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96926385063b70910e52bc803c50b20ef6c82400","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"三張分別係 正義逆 金幣女皇正 寶劍騎士逆<br />\n<br />\n似乎你地之間嘅條件有一定差距喎，正義逆代表咗雙方處有差異，又或者對方並唔只得你一個對象，對你嘅付出有限。<br />\n<br />\n金幣女皇正顯示你對對方有唔少嘅期望，會想建立一段正式嘅關係，而你係經濟上對對方有幫助，可能你會買野送比佢，或者係你自己有些少經濟能力。<br />\n<br />\n不過寶劍騎士逆係代表一種唔認真嘅態度，佢對於感情嘅想法同你唔同，一齊咗都好可能會浪費咗你嘅一番好意，因此朋友止步係個較好嘅選擇。"},{"pid":"e0d5145d4fa825bc37732c0039e9440f17bd7b17","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d69a4efcf3ea3dad0144a3f2585190a531dd2233","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96926385063b70910e52bc803c50b20ef6c82400","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"三張分別係 正義逆 金幣女皇正 寶劍騎士逆<br />\n<br />\n似乎你地之間嘅條件有一定差距喎，正義逆代表咗雙方處有差異，又或者對方並唔只得你一個對象，對你嘅付出有限。<br />\n<br />\n金幣女皇正顯示你對對方有唔少嘅期望，會想建立一段正式嘅關係，而你係經濟上對對方有幫助，可能你會買野送比佢，或者係你自己有些少經濟能力。<br />\n<br />\n不過寶劍騎士逆係代表一種唔認真嘅態度，佢對於感情嘅想法同你唔同，一齊咗都好可能會浪費咗你嘅一番好意，因此朋友止步係個較好嘅選擇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac697cb3d2c64ddc631ab4663608d72227fe90e","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764baa10f30f4026da7281a03dfe24792440b115","tid":2129931,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"三張分別係寶劍八逆 力量逆 權杖三逆<br />\n<br />\n寶劍八逆係種自我心理上嘅突破，指你終於決定離開一個令你不滿意&amp;前境欠佳嘅環境，進入一個新嘅領域，係張反映行動同起因嘅牌。<br />\n<br />\n但力量逆顯示你對依件事其實唔夠自信，心入面好擔心自問能唔能夠做得好似以前咁好，而依種不習慣同憂慮會嚴重影響你嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n權杖三逆暗示你新嘅上司並唔係一個好好嘅boss，相處上有摩擦，又或者你嘅計劃會因外來因素而受打擊，你會感到失望甚至後悔，要想得到你過去嘅成就，你要先捱過依段時期。<br />\n<br />\n加油啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99a192b0705bb08b59334b5f118372ebcc058ae","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0d5145d4fa825bc37732c0039e9440f17bd7b17","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d69a4efcf3ea3dad0144a3f2585190a531dd2233","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96926385063b70910e52bc803c50b20ef6c82400","tid":2129931,"uid":4941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"三張分別係 正義逆 金幣女皇正 寶劍騎士逆<br />\n<br />\n似乎你地之間嘅條件有一定差距喎，正義逆代表咗雙方處有差異，又或者對方並唔只得你一個對象，對你嘅付出有限。<br />\n<br />\n金幣女皇正顯示你對對方有唔少嘅期望，會想建立一段正式嘅關係，而你係經濟上對對方有幫助，可能你會買野送比佢，或者係你自己有些少經濟能力。<br />\n<br />\n不過寶劍騎士逆係代表一種唔認真嘅態度，佢對於感情嘅想法同你唔同，一齊咗都好可能會浪費咗你嘅一番好意，因此朋友止步係個較好嘅選擇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"希望你嘅答案會帶比你好嘅結果"},{"pid":"caf929bc195d695572d155d1ebeafd79403b95a4","tid":2129931,"uid":363634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547674708cb1a999fc1f615b20c2c1a21bb8bc6b","tid":2129931,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caf929bc195d695572d155d1ebeafd79403b95a4","tid":2129931,"uid":363634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:16:37.000Z","m